Transcript: Good evening. This is Margaret Bou, chair of T Motto Orleans. On behalf of T Motto Orleans, I wish to invite you to join us as a barbecue this Saturday, October first from eleven thirty to two PM at the Orleans client servant center on Central Boulevard. This event is open to all members of the community, so please come and have a verbiage with us. Volunteer donations on behalf of the Canadian Red Cross in support of the victim of hurricanes Katrina and Rita will be accepted. I look forward to meeting with you there.
